name: SAFABS 3: A FNAF Fan Game
description:
You are a nightguard at Fred and Bob Diner! The thing is, the animatronics have a tendency to move around at night. We don't know the exact reason why, but stay in your office and put on the "Fred" animatronic suit. S

Survive till' 7am to win

Bob, John Guy, Mr. Producer Guy: They will travel in the cameras. If you hear their music, put on the "Fred" spring lock suit.

Dave: He will stay in Camera 3. Check his camera every once in a while.

Now there are some places that you cannot see on the camera, so if you do not see an animatronic, they are probably travelling to the next camera. Or they are in your office
